></path></svg></span></div></div></a><a href="/essays/julian-s-huxley-the-man-who-put-eugenics-into-unesco"><div class="sc-c0f26063-7 jQxQLA"><div type="essay" class="sc-31fe189a-2 gUHfgD"><img alt="Black-and-white photo of a man in a suit holding a mug, sitting next to a chimpanzee in an enclosure." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyimages-613504200.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/0a2e1ccf-a263-4bbe-9641-044dfa524aba/essay-gettyima